label: PowerSystemResource
comment: A power system resource (PSR) can be an item of equipment such as a switch, an equipment container containing many individual items of equipment such as a substation, or an organisational entity such as sub-control area. Power system resources can have measurements associated.

label: Location
comment: The place, scene, or point of something where someone or something has been, is, and/or will be at a given moment in time. It can be defined with one or more position points (coordinates) in a given coordinate system.

label: WorkLocation
comment: Information about a particular location for various forms of work.

label: ServiceLocation
comment: A real estate location, commonly referred to as premises.
